==English==

===Etymology===

A portmonteau of the words ''[[hush]]'' and ''[[lullaby]].''

===Pronunciation===
Rhymes with [[lullaby]].

===Interjection===
'''hushaby'''

# {{archaic}} hush and be still. A [[lull]] to [[sleep]].

